<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Karell</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-07-31 14:12:58</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Yes its from Old Sebilis off a Froggy.<BR>
<BR>
Yes its worth 10K, far more actually. I saw one on Brell trade straight across for Eboots (14k).<BR>
<BR>
Mana and AC are far more important than anything else once your primary stat is maxed (Int/Wis). At 51 I have 202 Wis with +95 Mana gear on. For comparison, that 95 Mana equates to 9 Wis at level 51. This item is one of the top three AC/Mana items for the shoulder slot, and it is is All/All, so every caster and hybrid will want it (or should), at ANY level. It's even light enough for Monks to wear, who typically have little to wear in the shoulder slot that gives any real AC.<BR>
<BR>
This is far superior than nearly any other shoulder piece for any level caster or hybrid. That +25 mana equates to +5 wis/int at level 25, and +10 at level 12! So are we all on the same page now?<BR>
</font></td></tr></table>
